  /usr/src/libxcb1-<VER>-<REL>.tar.bz2

Or use 'cygport libxcb-<VER>-<REL>.cygport prep' to get a patched 
source directory.

To find out the files included in each binary package, you can
use "cygcheck -l <PKG>".

-------------------------------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.1-2 -----
Rebuilt with better usage of builtin getaddrinfo.
Created separate packages for each library.

----- version 1.1-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 1.0-3 -----
Rebuilt with builtin libgetaddrinfo to avoid extra dependencies.

----- version 1.0-2 -----
Rebuilt against shared libgetaddrinfo instead of including sources.

----- version 1.0-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin for X11R7.2.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://x.cygwin.com/
